Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.96,0:00:22.21,Default,,0,0,20,,Two shockingly beautiful eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:27.52,Default,,0,0,20,,A startling romance
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.52,0:00:29.73,Default,,0,0,20,,All-consuming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.73,0:00:31.90,Default,,0,0,20,,Inescapable
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.90,0:00:36.32,Default,,0,0,20,,With a Taishou Era dame
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.57,0:00:40.70,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.70,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,20,,Whose winning heart lavishes kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.42,0:00:49.46,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.46,0:00:53.84,Default,,0,0,20,,Whose winning heart lavishes kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.84,0:00:58.10,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.47,Default,,0,0,20,,High, High, High, High Collar Lady's coming
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.47,0:01:06.81,Default,,0,0,20,,Whose winning heart lavishes kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,60,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.04,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me a High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that period
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.50,0:23:48.49,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with people I love
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.72,0:23:57.31,Default,,0,0,20,,I just want to know what's in his heart, \Nwhile he goes away{added} I want him to turn around,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.31,0:24:00.18,Default,,0,0,60,,to give me once again this loving glance
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.18,0:24:05.69,Default,,0,0,20,,Ah, how frustrating it is \Nto have this unrequited feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.69,0:24:10.64,Default,,0,0,60,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.15,0:24:16.83,Default,,0,0,60,,Just a tomboyish lady with a smidgen of pretension
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.79,0:24:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs30\pos(687.568,500)\blur0.667\bord0}\h Translation    alucardnoyuuutsu\h\N\h       Timing    Perevodildo         \h\NQC    Ziusudra\h
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.81,0:01:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,After getting into a fight, Benio used her tomboyish sword technique{売られた喧嘩を買ったはいいがさえにさえたるじゃじゃうま一刀流}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.44,0:01:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and blew the masterfully experienced count away.{老伯爵の天狗の花おもののみごとにへし折って}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.76,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, these two started to celebrate Benio's imminent return.{これで紅緒は追い出されると男2人は宇宙展}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.39,0:01:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But hold on,{ところがどっこい}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the count saw his long-gone son's look in Benio's eyes and liked it,{老伯爵は紅緒の\N瞳が死んだ我が子と同じだったとお気に召す}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.63,0:01:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, he was even cured by Benio's special Chinese herbal medicine.{かてて加えてまごころこもった漢方薬に老人の心は心のみ}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.51,0:01:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,All of a sudden, the counts' mutual love came to light,{以外嫌以外伯爵夫婦は互いに深く愛し合っていることが明るみに出た}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.43,0:01:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,while Benio is being forced to accept her arranged marriage,{それに引き換え我が許婚押しつけられた結婚に甘んじるとは}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.05,0:01:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,but she won't ever give in!{それでも男が許せない！}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.78,0:01:58.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,300)\c&HF3ECE6&\pos(467.027,93.333)\bord0\blur0.667\fs60\b1}Episode 11\NWelcome to the party of grief
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much for today's training.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.09,0:02:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome. Be sure to perfect that technique for the next rehearsal.{いいえ来月のおさらい会までにはさっきのところきっちりと揚げといてくださいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.03,0:02:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.76,0:02:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.24,0:02:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.08,0:02:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,it's Fujieda Ranmaru, the young kabuki dancer!{若手歌舞伎ふじえだらんまるよ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.87,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's fabulous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.70,0:02:43.91,Default,,0,0,666,,And a young teacher too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.56,Default,,0,0,666,,Please, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.63,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.36,0:02:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,- Wait!\N- Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.02,0:03:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Young teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.50,0:03:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.18,0:03:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, poor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even go out of classes in peace anymore.{うっかりお稽古にも出られやしないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are all girls the same?{どうして女って皆あんなのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.26,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If they are anyone but Benio...{僕も絶対\紅緒さん以外の女の子なんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A delicious man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.40,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm done!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.02,0:03:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:56.82,Default,,0,0,666,,Ranmaru!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.82,0:03:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:03.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't touch me, it's embarrassing!{いや寄せったなおいらでみっともねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,First of all, how did you miss me if we meet everyday?{第一懐かしいとって毎日毎日会ってるじゃねえか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still missed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.99,0:04:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me! I'm not interested in those things.{寄せよつられてその気になるではないか}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.71,0:04:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What does that mean, Ushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.03,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, nothin' special.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ushi, how's Benio?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.34,0:04:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss has completely changed,{あの男勝りの親分がすっかり変わっちまって}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.26,0:04:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she's worn out and lost her will.{えらくまあげっそりとやつれちまって}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Moving to a noble mansion out of the blue...{べにおさん慣れない公家やしきなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.12,0:04:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,was too hard for her, after all.{やっぱり無理だったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to do something about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.05,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushi, please go see her at the mansion,{うしさん、伯爵家へ行って様子を見てきてちょうだい}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.92,0:04:41.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.{僕なんだか胸騒ぎがするの}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've done it,{そんなこと言ったっておめぇ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.14,0:04:45.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's Sunday,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.82,0:04:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so I don't have to get her to school.{女学校へお供する必要はないんだぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.58,0:04:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you won't do it?{じゃ、僕の頼みを聞けないって言うの？}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, if that's the case, I have another plan!{そう、それならそっちにも覚悟があるから}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.28,0:04:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.52,0:04:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.57,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.23,0:05:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're way too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.53,0:05:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.16,0:05:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I'll go, now calm down!{寄せ寄せ、行くよ、行きゃいいんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.99,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is why Ushi is the best!{だからうしさんって大好き}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.64,0:05:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.63,0:05:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are they getting ready for?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A celebration.{園遊会}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A celebration, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.93,0:05:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.96,0:05:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I only invited my circle of friends.{僕の友達ばかりのうちわのパーティーですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They all said that they wanted to see you,{みんな僕の婚約者を見たい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.92,0:05:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,they're all excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.06,0:05:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't wanna!{そんな困ります}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I am your fiancee, uhm...{婚約者と言っても、あの。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.79,0:05:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.05,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've still not agreed to this marriage.{あの、アタシはまだ結婚を承知したわけでは。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so stiff about it, Benio.{そんなに堅苦しく考える必要はないんですよ紅緒さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.23,0:06:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't just ignore my point of view!{アタシにだって立場ってもんがあんたかね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.47,0:06:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is he always so selfish!?{何度も自分本位に決めてしまうんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.03,0:06:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.17,0:06:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.28,0:06:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.60,0:06:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.00,0:06:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Boss is mad about something.{どうやら親分が今日は荒れ模様だな\Nうーん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.92,0:06:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru's feminine intuition was right.{蘭丸の女性的な感は大したもん}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.65,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a male, but whatever, I need to inform him.{あいつは男だったがともかく知らせてこなくちゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.20,0:06:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Ushigorou, right?{もしうしごろさんでしたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in a rush, so I'll see ya later.{なんか呼んだら後にしてくんな}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't wait anymore.{いいえもう待てません}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.22,0:06:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you being too harsh?{おいきついお言葉じゃねえかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.43,0:06:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I'm just doing my job!{はい私の職業はかかっておりますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatcha sayin'!? Whaddya mean by this?{なんだと何を言いちゃも----}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou, please stop carrying Lady Benio to school on your rickshaw!{うしごろうさん、べにおさまを人力者で学校へ送り迎えするのは\やめてください}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh!? Why would I listen to ya?{----}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.20,0:07:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,She is a very important lady for this family,{あの方はご当家にとって大切なお人です}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.32,0:07:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, it's plain obvious that I have to escort her with the Ijuuins' car!{さすれば私が伊集院家のこの車で送り迎えさせていただく のが理の当然}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard! Are you stealing my job!?{やろうめ！おいらに手を引けてのかよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.80,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, if you agree quickly.{早く申せばその通りです}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.12,0:07:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the difference between agreeing quickly and slowly, you idiot!?{早く申し立て遅く申し立て同じだよこの馬鹿野郎}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you've agreed!{ではご了承願いましたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! You're just trying to spread discord between me and Boss,{うるさい親分とおいらの間に水をさそったって}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it's no good!{そうはいかねえぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a rush, so we'll set things straight later!{こしたら急いでるんだ後で落とし前をつけるからな}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.91,0:07:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That damn punk...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,They should be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.69,0:07:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Whassup!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.66,0:07:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu, where's your fiancee?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She's called Benio, right? C'mon, introduce her to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is your beautiful Mädchen? {どこだその麗しのメッチェン - I wanted to keep the German reference}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.96,0:08:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she the one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.91,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Beautiful?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.26,0:08:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you were into these things.{お前この趣味だったのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.14,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Lolita complex, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.28,0:08:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lolita complex, heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.75,0:08:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.75,0:08:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Lolita complex,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.05,0:08:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and borderline boys' love on top of it.{すなわち少年愛に通じる}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.58,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.38,0:08:28.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Whadja say!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.86,0:08:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.59,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wanted to praise you.{実は褒めたつもりなんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, this is Takayashiki, a buddy of mine.{べにおさんこちら僕の親友で高屋敷です}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.45,0:08:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's sharp-tongued, but he's a nice guy.{口は悪いがいいやつですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.96,0:08:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He was really mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.06,0:08:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.20,0:08:45.27,Default,,0,0,0,,And here, it's the same Known-not Fellow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.40,0:08:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,An outdoor celebration?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.28,0:08:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.49,0:08:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, there are many people, there, right?{じゃ、大勢の人が集まるのね}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.23,0:09:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably. I hope Boss won't feel too awkward there.{多分な親分がうまく立ち回ってくるといいんだけどね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.25,0:09:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,She's not so good with social skills.{あんまり社交は上手な方じゃねえからなうちの親分は}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.34,0:09:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's a celebration, there'll also be alcohol, right?{それと園遊会といえばお酒も出るんでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.28,0:09:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.17,0:09:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.11,0:09:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss had that unknown inclination!{うちの親分知らんの傾向があったっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's terrible! I gotta do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.29,0:09:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru, think of something!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.98,0:09:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to me! I've got a wonderful idea!{任せといて、素晴らしいアイディアがひらめいたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll work for sure!{こうしちゃ入れられないと}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.01,0:09:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know his plans, but it should be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.60,0:09:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.77,0:09:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Takayashiki Kaname and he wants to be a poet.{この高屋敷要は文士くずれでね}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,His nickname is Lion.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.88,0:09:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lion?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.14,0:10:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can kind of understand
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.30,0:10:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.72,0:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for inviting me, Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.28,0:10:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's the beautiful Tamaki!{いやいや、麗しの環殿}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.53,0:10:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Our angel!{我らの天使}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.68,0:10:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddess!{女神ちゃん}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.72,0:10:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.66,0:10:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, come with me for a second.{べにおさんもその後いかがお少し}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.96,0:10:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.65,0:10:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that request?{何をその気取った挨拶}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, what happened to your breaking mission? {べにお、どうしたのよ例の作戦}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.08,0:10:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a fight going on and enemy won't give up.{ただいま実行中なるの敵もてごわし}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.60,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a tough one.{我苦戦なり}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.85,0:10:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.71,0:10:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll try my best.{でも頑張ってみるわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.24,0:10:49.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.09,0:10:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh-oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.92,0:10:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This conversation is sure getting lively.{話が弾んでるようですなクラスメイト同士}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Benio is telling me a lot of gossip about the count.{ええ、べにお様から色々と伯爵家の噂などを伺っておりましたの}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.64,0:11:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, you two,{さあさあお二人さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.08,0:11:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,don't be shy and join us!{女同士そんなところが固まっていないで}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.53,0:11:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we play a game?{ゲームでもしませんか}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.75,0:11:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, I wrote a poem for you.{環さんあなたに捧げる詩を書いたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.89,0:11:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.96,0:11:19.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll read it later.{後で拝見させていただくわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.91,0:11:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Later, huh.{後で、か}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.43,0:11:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You got rejected twice, huh?{また振られたなお前}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.22,0:11:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Unrequited love is real love,{忍ぶ恋こそ至極なり」}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.75,0:11:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll write a good poem.{いい詩ができそうだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.{今日はよくいらっしゃいました}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Enjoy your time here.{ゆっくりと楽しんでくださいね}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.18,0:11:44.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.60,0:12:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.23,0:12:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.31,0:12:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,there's something I want to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How long are you going to detain Benio?{いつまで紅を引き止めとくつもり}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.23,0:12:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I know everything.{私知ってますのよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.29,0:12:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll marry Benio just because of your grandmother.{あなたがおばあ様の言いつけで愛してもいないべにおと}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.12,0:12:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're engaged...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio won't fall for you.{べにはあなたに向いてなわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.70,0:12:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.05,0:12:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,There must be someone who's better suited for you.{趣味も環境もあなたにはもっとぴったりした人がいるはずよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.01,0:12:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel bad for Benio?{それにべにおだって可哀想}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:47.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggling in this mansion all of a sudden...{こんな慣れない公家の家なんかで苦労して}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.56,0:12:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's talking about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?{公家の家か}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.56,0:12:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.{そうだね確かに}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.77,0:13:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're noble too.{そして君もN家族の生まれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.68,0:13:03.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki, you see...{環さんそれなんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just because we were born in this place,{僕たちは偶然ここに生まれ合わせただけで}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.31,0:13:15.19,Default,,0,0,0,,we have the privilege of being nobles.{それだけで華族という特権を持っている}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.68,0:13:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we live with it.{それを振りかざして生きているんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.36,0:13:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to run away from this strange world.{僕は逃れたいと思ってきたいつもいつもこの奇妙な世界から}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.59,0:13:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But ever since I met Benio,{でも紅緒さんに会ってから}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.22,0:13:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I started to think that I could cross this boundary someday.{いつか僕もその垣根を越えることができるかもしれない}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.87,0:13:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I began to think like that.{そう思うようになった}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.57,0:13:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a girl that could turn her dreams into reality.{彼女は夢を見てその夢を現実にすることのできる人だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.44,0:13:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Unlike her, I only dream and do nothing.{ただ夢を見ているだけの僕とは違うんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.15,0:13:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, at first I only wanted to do it for my grandmother.{確かに僕も最初はおばあ様のためにと考えていた}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.85,0:13:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But things have changed.{でも今は違う}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio has such a mysterious charm,{べにおさんはそんな不思議な魅力のある娘}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never met a girl like her.{あんな子を見たのは初めてさ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.89,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu, deep down you've always wanted someone like Benio.{忍さん、心のどこかでいつもべにおを望んでいたのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.31,0:14:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll never persuade him.{入り込む余地なんてなさそう}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.59,0:14:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand you now.{わかったわしのぶさんの気持ち}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.30,0:14:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a fantastic girl, so you'll definitely find a fantastic-{君だって素晴らしいお嬢さんだよきっと素晴らしい相手が}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.47,0:14:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.53,0:14:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I... have given up.{私諦めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is my best friend.{べにおは私の親友ですからね}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.74,0:14:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever make her sad, I...{あの人を不幸せにしたら私が承知。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.26,0:14:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forgive you!{承知しませんよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.13,0:14:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, lord, where did those two go?{しょうがないな2人ともどこ行っちゃったのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.59,0:15:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shinobu! He's never done something like that to me!{少尉ったらあんなこと私には一度だってしてくれたことないんだから}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is she better than me?{差がついてる}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.95,0:15:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What could those two be talking about?{あの2人何話してるんだろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki is so beautiful...{綺麗だなたまき}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Tamaki's better suited for Shinobu than me.{少尉には環の方が私よりずっと似合うの}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.43,0:15:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Whaddya want? What did I do?{なんだって言うんだ俺が何をしたってんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?{どうしたって言うんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.01,0:15:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.47,0:15:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.48,0:15:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, cut it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?{どうしたんだ一体}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.18,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know. These dogs should know Takayashiki pretty well.{わからんこの犬は高屋敷をよく知ってるはずなんだが}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.03,0:15:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu, do something!{おい伊集院なんとかしろよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been in this house many times,{僕はこの家へなんでも来てるし}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.30,0:16:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've never been barked at like this!{こんなに吠えられる覚えはないぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.84,0:16:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio, don't you believe my friends?{べにお、僕の親友の人柄を信じてくれないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But I trust these two's pure insinct too.{でも私はこの2匹の汚れのない本能を信じます}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They must be sensing something strange about Takayashiki just today.{今日に限って\N高屋敷さんに吠えるのは何か異常を感じているからです}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.16,0:16:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But I don't know what it is.{しかし僕は覚えがないよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.80,0:16:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe these dogs. Tenmaru, Chimaru...{私は犬を信じます。てんまる、ちまる。。。}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.63,0:16:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You two! Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.65,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.83,0:16:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, bark!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.87,0:16:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hush, hush, hush, I'm telling you to hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!\NBenio, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.17,0:17:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Tenmaru, Chimaru, hush!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.44,0:17:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? They listen to Benio more than me.{なんということだ僕よりも紅緒さんの言うことを聞くなんて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.34,0:17:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.{
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.41,0:17:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takayashiki, there's something on your back.{おい高屋敷お前の背中に何かいるぜ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.72,0:17:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,A wasp!{クマンバチだ - technically a carpenter bee}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.54,0:17:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.37,0:17:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't taken a bath in ten days,{俺は十日も風呂に入ってないんだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be doomed if I get stung!{刺したってバッチリよー}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.26,0:17:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Good grief!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That sure was a close call!{あいつに刺されたらえらいことだからな}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.50,0:17:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're such good dogs! So you weren't barking at Takayashiki, but at the wasp.{いい子ね、高屋敷じゃなくて、はちに吠えていた}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, they're so smart!{しかし賢いのだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.16,0:17:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Better than military ones!{軍用権以上だ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.74,0:17:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.98,0:17:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.82,0:17:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked for another reason.{僕は別のことの方がショックだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:17:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I raised Tenmaru and Chimaru since they were puppies,{てんまるとちまるは僕は子犬の頃から仕込んだんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.89,0:18:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was astonished that they listen to Benio more than me.{その僕よりもべにおさんの言うことを聞くんだから参った}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I thought it would end badly.{いや一度はどうなるかと思ったよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.16,0:18:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you haven't taken a bath in ten days?{お前十日も風呂に入っていないんだって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so dirty, at least have a shower.{汚い人ねシャワーでも浴びてらっしゃいよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.60,0:18:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you say so, Tamaki...{たまきさんがそうおっしゃるのなら}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.80,0:18:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.78,0:18:20.47,Default,,0,0,0,,She's pretty good, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.47,0:18:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She just tamed those two dogs,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.21,0:18:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but I won't be tamed!{じゃが儂はそうはいかんぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:48.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, really, Benio always surprises me.{いや全く紅緒さんにはいつも驚かされてしまうんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.90,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, everyone,{いや諸君すまなかったね}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I spoiled the party because of my carelessness.{僕の不注意からパーティーをぶち壊してしまって}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.88,0:18:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're brand new!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.01,0:18:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,For real.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.39,0:19:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, shall we drink?{さあ、飲み直しますか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.64,0:19:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.44,0:19:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hell yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am deeply sorry, but I'll be leaving now.{私せっかくだけどお先に失礼いたします}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.98,0:19:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Tamaki, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.65,0:19:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not feeling too well.{ちょっと気分が優れないもので}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. It's a pity.\NThen, I'll escort you with my car.{そうか残念だなじゃあうちの車で送らせるよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.55,0:19:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,T-Then I'll see you off.{よし僕は送ろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.47,0:19:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tamaki, is it okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.78,0:19:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, why not!{私でよければどうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Riding with the beautiful Tamaki...{麗しのたまき殿と相乗りか}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.46,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I entrust you my car. {車頼むよ玉城さんがお帰りなんだお送りしてくれ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.29,0:20:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright then, get in.{さあどうぞお乗りください}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.99,0:20:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.46,0:20:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.53,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A rickshaw is such a fancy vehicle.{人力車とはこれはまた風流な}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.51,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I know right? That looks fun!{そうねそちらの方が面白そうだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.31,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.39,0:20:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.85,0:20:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hop in, hop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.85,0:20:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm always happy to help Boss's friends!{N親分の友達だったら喜んでね}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.31,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.40,0:20:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ushigorou!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.18,0:20:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,In this male-dominated world isn't this treating her as a property?{男立ての世界では縄張りということを何よりも重んずるの -  I don't really know what she meant by this}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.25,0:20:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood, Boss.{わかりやした親分}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:57.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't escort you home anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.46,0:21:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please get in that car.{あっちの自動車でどうぞ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.51,0:21:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, but I wanted to ride it once.{あら度乗ってみたかったのに}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.18,0:21:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, okay?{運転士さんご厄介になりますよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.05,0:21:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.10,0:21:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Lady Benio!{this series really lives up to that line from OP "with her kind heart, winning everyone over xD - perevodildo}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.64,0:21:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,After the dogs, she won the chauffeur over!{犬の次は運転手を味方につけましたよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.61,0:21:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Be honest, you've grown fond of her.{本当は気に入ったとおっしゃりたいのでしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The hell are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.93,0:21:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.34,0:21:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't Sunday my day off on my schedule?{スケジュール日曜日でお休みじゃないの}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.21,0:21:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about a different thing.{それとは別口でちょっとご相談が}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.73,0:21:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.82,0:21:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.28,0:21:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?{何かしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.41,0:21:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, you see...{はいそれがその}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.74,0:21:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The new maid said that she wanted to {新しく入ったメイドがどうしてもべにお様づきにしてくれと申しまして}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,A new maid?{新しいメイドが}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.02,0:21:54.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.92,0:21:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.81,0:21:58.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.26,0:22:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,From today onwards, you'll be serving Lady Benio.{今日からこちらのべにお様があなたのご主人様ですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.40,0:22:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Greet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.66,0:22:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Ranko, I'm glad to meet you, Master.{らんこと申しますよろしくお願いしますご主人様}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.27,0:22:19.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wha-Wha-?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranmaru!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.09,0:22:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,An unexpected guy in a unexpected place,{とんでもないところへとんでもないやつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.07,0:22:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,the tormented Ranmaru,{思いつめた蘭丸が}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.99,0:22:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,desperately wants to help,{是非ともお役に立ちたいと}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.45,0:22:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,with her feminine dedication-{女心を一筋}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.71,0:22:36.93,Default,,0,0,0,,or should I say masculine dedication?{いや、男心というべきかな}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.93,0:22:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How will things go with Ranko, our newcomer?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The tormented Ranmaru, who's now a maid in disguise,{悩ましの美少女がメイドに化けた蘭丸で}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.48,0:23:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wants to help Benio, with his inconvenient support,{是非ともお役に立ちたいとはた迷惑な応援}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.46,0:23:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,but he must not reveal his true sex.{だが男女のその正体がもしもバレたら一大事に}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As usual, the count's keen look{さすが老伯爵の慧眼は}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.63,0:23:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,will question Ranmaru's true identity.{鋭く蘭丸の素性を問い詰めた}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What's next? Big trouble.{さあどうなる大ピンチ}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.96,0:23:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time on Here Comes Smart-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.92,0:23:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Dance, tormented beauty,{踊れ悩ましの美少女}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.40,0:23:19.60,Default,,0,0,0,,don't miss it!
